              "text_rFkCBG": {
                "type": "text",
                "name": "Text",
                "settings": {
                  "visibility": "always-display",
                  "text": "<p>For decades, we’ve been told that <strong>\"hustle culture\" is the key to success</strong>, but no one talks about the <strong>biological tax</strong> it levies on our very existence. We are currently living through a silent epidemic of time-poverty, where the human brain is constantly redlining, trying to squeeze <strong>a 48-hour mental load into a body that demands a massive 8-hour \"shutdown\"</strong> just to function. We aren't just tired; we are being robbed of our prime years by a prehistoric biological requirement.</p>",
                  "alignment": "left",
