              "text_YQNDkX": {
                "type": "text",
                "name": "Text",
                "settings": {
                  "visibility": "always-display",
                  "text": "<p>It feels like a losing battle. You <strong>stay up late</strong> to <strong>finish a project</strong> or <strong>catch a moment of peace</strong>, only to <strong>pay for it with a \"brain fog\"</strong> that <strong>ruins the next fourteen hours</strong>. We are stuck in a loop of sacrificing our health for our dreams, or our dreams for our health.</p>",
