          "text_HK8jKJ": {
            "type": "text",
            "settings": {
              "visibility": "always-display",
              "text": "<p>The Chrono-Nap™ is a localized temporal-dilation engine designed to compress a standard 8-hour regenerative sleep cycle into a 20-minute neurological window.</p><p>By fundamentally restructuring your neural recovery path, the Chrono-Nap™ allows you to achieve 100% cellular and cognitive repair in the mere time it takes to finish a morning coffee. It works by intelligently skipping the inefficient \"light sleep\" filler that plagues traditional rest, instead catapulting your brain directly into a state of high-intensity neuro-regeneration.</p><p>While in this hyper-lucid state, you can utilize the Dream-Stream interface to passively absorb complex information or master new skills at an accelerated rate. You’ll emerge through precise temporal calibration—waking up without a hint of \"sleep inertia\" and feeling as though you’ve just enjoyed a long, restful Saturday morning. Ultimately, this compact recovery system allows you to reclaim over 2,500 hours of \"lost life\" every single year, giving you back the time that biology used to steal.</p>",
