              "text_drBrB6": {
                "type": "text",
                "name": "Text",
                "settings": {
                  "visibility": "always-display",
                  "text": "<p>The Chrono-Nap™ was designed specifically for those who find the standard 24-hour day fundamentally insufficient. If you are an <strong>overachiever</strong> with more ambitious goals than the clock allows, this technology provides the ultimate competitive edge by extending your window of peak performance. For the <strong>new parent</strong> struggling to survive on the fragments of \"broken sleep,\" it offers a way to restore full cognitive function in just minutes, while <strong>lifelong learners</strong> can finally master new skills through the Dream-Stream interface while the body rests. Ultimately, if you are a <strong>visionary</strong> who feels like life is moving too fast—or if you simply want to actually live the thousands of hours usually surrendered to the pillow—then you are the perfect match for this temporal revolution.<br/><br/>This isn't merely about buying a piece of technology; it’s about choosing to opt out of a biological limitation that has held humanity back since the dawn of time. We are standing at a unique crossroads where the friction between our physical needs and our limitless potential can finally be smoothed away. Every moment you spend waiting is another hour of your life that you will never get back—a literal sacrifice to the pillow. By integrating the Chrono-Nap™ into your daily rhythm, you aren't just gaining rest; you are gaining a lifetime of extra years to build, love, and experience everything the world has to offer. The question is no longer whether you can afford to change how you sleep, but whether you can afford to keep losing a third of your existence to a cycle you’ve already outgrown.</p>",
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "mobile_alignment": "mobile-left",
                  "text_size": 14,
