          "text_M9Az4U": {
            "type": "text",
            "settings": {
              "visibility": "always-display",
              "text": "<p>The information provided in this article is for educational and informational purposes only and describes the emerging field of localized temporal dilation. While the Chrono-Nap™ has undergone rigorous internal testing and independent neuro-sync validation, it is important to understand that temporal compression technology interacts with the human circadian rhythm in ways that vary by individual. Users should strictly adhere to the \"Temporal Wake\" protocols to ensure a seamless transition between dilated and non-dilated states.</p><p>Please be advised that the Chrono-Nap™ is classified as a \"Biological Optimization Device\" and is not intended to diagnose, treat, or cure chronic sleep disorders. While 98% of users report significant cognitive enhancement, the technology requires a 48-hour \"Neural Mapping\" period upon first use to calibrate the Dream-Stream interface to your specific brainwave signature. Misalignment during this calibration phase may result in vivid dreaming or a temporary sense of displaced time.</p><p>By utilizing this device, the user acknowledges that the \"Life-Extension Loophole\" refers to the cognitive reclamation of time typically lost to sleep and does not imply an extension of maximum biological lifespan beyond natural human limits. Chrono-Systems Research Group is not responsible for the sudden influx of productivity, the mastery of multiple languages, or any social friction caused by having significantly more \"waking hours\" than your peers.</p>",
